OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe end of the tricky      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'Korean age'               
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, South Koreans are set to become one or 
OL,6, even two years younger - at least on   
OL,7, official paperwork.                    
OL,9,FOn Thursday, the South Korean          
OL,10,Fparliament passed a law to scrap       
OL,11,FKorea's two traditional methods of     
OL,12,Fcounting age.                          
OL,14,FFrom June 2023, the so-called "Korean  
OL,15,FAge" system will no longer be permitted
OL,16,Fon official documents.                 
OL,18,FOnly the standardised, internationally 
OL,19,Frecognised method will remain.         
